&lt;p style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 19px; padding: 0px;"&gt;Curso de Captação de Recursos&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 19px; padding: 0px;"&gt;Dias 17, 18 e 19 de agosto.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 19px; padding: 0px;"&gt;Horário: Das 19h00 às 22h00&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 19px; padding: 0px;"&gt;Local: Salão Ingleses - Sede da Elase (Rua &lt;span style="font-size: x-small; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"&gt;Deputado Antônio Edu Vieira, 999 - Carvoeira - Florianópolis - ao lado da Eletrosul).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
